          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1624293655909-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained noodles</strong> to the pan with the sauce and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>lime & chilli noodles</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1624293661919-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1624293661919-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1624293661919-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1624293661919-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1624293661919-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve your <strong>lime & chilli noodles</strong> with the <strong>zingy salmon</strong> over the top</p><p>Tear over your<strong> coriander</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
